text: Chernovskoye () is a rural locality (a selo) and the administrative center of Chernovskoye Rural Settlement, Bolshesosnovsky District, Perm Krai, Russia. The population was 1,806 as of 2010. There are 25 streets. == Geography == It is located 23 km south from Bolshaya Sosnova. == References == Category:Rural localities in Bolshesosnovsky District
title: Chernovskoye, Perm Krai
